      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEY BUBBA LOUIE (4) got around 320m in a useful 18.24 when winning a Grade 5 at this track last start. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. JAMES ALARM (2) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 320m behind On A Dime (18.52) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and three minor placings from six starts. Cannot be taken lightly. BATGIRL (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 18.21 beating Mepunga Shine. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Likely to be in the finish.",
